data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 2-story gem, last rehabbed in 2020, boasts a perfect blend of timeless charm and modern amenities. Situated on a quiet Chatam street. This home is ideally situated within easy reach of local schools, parks, shopping centers, and all the amenities you need for everyday living. Commuting to work or exploring the city is a breeze with convenient access to major roads and public transportation.    Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautifully rehabbed home that perfectly combines modern living with a touch of character. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this house your new home!  With the bonus of low property taxes, this home offers an excellent opportunity to make the most of your investment.
